        "created_at": "2017-11-14T19:03:51.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I had a bottle of the same 2005 J.M. Boillot Puligny-Montrachet on October 10th and it was Horribly oxidized\u2026 I\u2019m glad to hear your was doing better than mine, and my point does not prove anything, but I still see it as a luck of the draw set up\u2026</p>",
