        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/r/ed8c4c/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2017-11-14T20:15:23.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>It is only that - a hypothesis. And I realise my sampling is far from statistically valid, though would be happy to correct that with lots of help <img src=\"/images/emoji/unicode/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\">! I\u2019m interested in what others have experienced, particularly where you have aged vintages from a producer up and down the hierarchy.</p>",
